1
00:00:11,300 --> 00:00:15,500
♪The human heart hatches schemes, stuck fast in the mire♪

2
00:00:15,580 --> 00:00:19,980
♪In the Judge's ledger, the accounts are settled♪

3
00:00:20,060 --> 00:00:24,340
♪Reckon the human face and the beastly deed. Count the debts of injustice♪

4
00:00:24,420 --> 00:00:28,700
♪Walking the dark path, pleading for moonlight♪

5
00:00:28,780 --> 00:00:33,100
♪The pitiful suffer, while the privileged command respect♪

6
00:00:33,180 --> 00:00:37,420
♪Pluck one hair, and the stench of sin runs through the skin♪

7
00:00:37,500 --> 00:00:41,780
♪Scoundrels have a form, while ghostly lies are intangible♪

8
00:00:41,820 --> 00:00:46,140
♪Looking inward brings no answer. Ask Heaven for mercy♪

9
00:00:46,180 --> 00:00:48,260
♪The book of sins is presented, proof of guilt recorded chapter after chapter♪

10
00:00:48,260 --> 00:00:50,380
♪Grant mercy, and ruin follows♪

11
00:00:50,420 --> 00:00:52,540
♪An inescapable net is cast. Look up in all four directions♪

12
00:00:52,540 --> 00:00:54,780
♪Retribution will follow♪

13
00:00:54,860 --> 00:00:56,900
♪Tigers, leopards, and wolves. Darkness laid bare♪

14
00:00:56,900 --> 00:00:59,140
♪Your mercy only serves to share the loot♪

15
00:00:59,220 --> 00:01:01,340
♪In the ledger of good and evil, words unfurl without end♪

16
00:01:01,340 --> 00:01:03,700
♪Heaven's way tolerates no wrongful judgment♪

17
00:01:07,900 --> 00:01:09,940
♪The book of sins is presented, proof of guilt recorded chapter after chapter♪

18
00:01:09,940 --> 00:01:12,100
♪Grant mercy, and ruin follows♪

19
00:01:12,140 --> 00:01:14,220
♪An inescapable net is cast. Look up in all four directions♪

20
00:01:14,220 --> 00:01:16,500
♪Retribution will follow♪

21
00:01:16,540 --> 00:01:18,580
♪Tigers, leopards, and wolves. Darkness laid bare♪

22
00:01:18,580 --> 00:01:20,860
♪Your mercy only serves to share the loot♪

23
00:01:20,940 --> 00:01:23,060
♪In the ledger of good and evil, words unfurl without end♪

24
00:01:23,060 --> 00:01:24,220
♪Heaven's way tolerates no wrongful judgment♪

25
00:01:24,300 --> 00:01:25,980
[Adapted from a Shuqi.com novel]

26
00:01:25,980 --> 00:01:27,480
[Original Author: Senlin Lu]

27
00:01:27,480 --> 00:01:29,980
[Unveil: Jadewind]

28
00:01:30,300 --> 00:01:32,980
[Episode 33]

29
00:01:36,390 --> 00:01:38,320
The Ceremony finally ended without a hitch.

30
00:01:38,550 --> 00:01:39,980
You've worked hard these days, Deputy Director Xiao.

31
00:01:40,640 --> 00:01:41,450
Let's enjoy

32
00:01:41,880 --> 00:01:42,680
tonight's Grand Festival.

33
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:46,860
Not yet.

34
00:01:49,600 --> 00:01:50,890
The Grand Festival is the main event.

35
00:02:06,550 --> 00:02:07,580
You're here early.

36
00:02:07,830 --> 00:02:08,730
For tonight's Grand Festival,

37
00:02:09,110 --> 00:02:10,490
is everything in place?

38
00:02:11,360 --> 00:02:11,930
Look.

39
00:02:12,520 --> 00:02:14,170
Am I going to be your groom,

40
00:02:14,430 --> 00:02:15,700
or your household servant?

41
00:02:15,990 --> 00:02:17,050
The last time I entered the palace

42
00:02:17,320 --> 00:02:18,450
was twenty years ago.

43
00:02:20,110 --> 00:02:20,770
What's your plan?

44
00:02:22,150 --> 00:02:23,540
Just get me into the palace,

45
00:02:23,960 --> 00:02:25,260
and keep me out of sight.

46
00:02:25,590 --> 00:02:26,300
I'll handle

47
00:02:26,590 --> 00:02:27,450
everything else.

48
00:02:28,760 --> 00:02:29,490
Don't worry.

49
00:02:30,240 --> 00:02:31,140
I give you my word:

50
00:02:31,590 --> 00:02:32,330
this time,

51
00:02:33,040 --> 00:02:34,820
I'll avenge the Prince of Duan.

52
00:02:35,270 --> 00:02:36,860
You trust him that much?

53
00:02:38,270 --> 00:02:39,490
It's already past Shen Hour.

54
00:02:40,080 --> 00:02:41,100
Go rest a bit.

55
00:02:41,480 --> 00:02:43,300
We'll be busy again soon.

56
00:02:57,270 --> 00:02:58,420
Just as I thought.

57
00:02:58,920 --> 00:03:00,020
So you're here too, Mr. Xiao.

58
00:03:00,520 --> 00:03:02,170
You already knew the Celestial Lord was him.

59
00:03:02,520 --> 00:03:03,380
Why hide it?

60
00:03:03,960 --> 00:03:05,300
Because what he did

61
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:06,930
is what I wanted to do too.

62
00:03:11,760 --> 00:03:12,330
Come with me.

63
00:03:12,590 --> 00:03:13,540
You shouldn't be here.

64
00:03:13,710 --> 00:03:14,420
Why?

65
00:03:16,200 --> 00:03:17,330
Because I wasn't supposed to find

66
00:03:17,330 --> 00:03:18,610
you were in on it with the Celestial Lord,

67
00:03:18,870 --> 00:03:20,730
or discover you were behind the palace lantern case,

68
00:03:20,740 --> 00:03:22,410
or use an investigation

69
00:03:22,410 --> 00:03:23,650
to bring you to justice?

70
00:03:24,920 --> 00:03:26,050
You think you're clever, huh?

71
00:03:27,270 --> 00:03:27,890
Fine.

72
00:03:28,800 --> 00:03:30,300
Then tell me

73
00:03:30,870 --> 00:03:32,770
how you discovered I was behind it.

74
00:03:33,430 --> 00:03:34,650
At first, I thought

75
00:03:34,800 --> 00:03:36,930
the killer hid near the lantern,

76
00:03:37,240 --> 00:03:38,860
and cut the cord when no one watched.

77
00:03:39,270 --> 00:03:40,380
But I missed one thing.

78
00:03:40,870 --> 00:03:42,580
The room was lit up everywhere.

79
00:03:42,640 --> 00:03:44,170
There was nowhere to hide.

80
00:03:44,710 --> 00:03:46,260
And around Lang Maochun,

81
00:03:46,590 --> 00:03:47,610
there was only him alone.

82
00:03:48,360 --> 00:03:49,330
If it wasn't him,

83
00:03:50,240 --> 00:03:51,420
then only you could have cut it,

84
00:03:51,500 --> 00:03:53,170
as you were closest to him.

85
00:03:53,320 --> 00:03:53,730
I...

86
00:03:54,430 --> 00:03:55,330
I didn't do it.

87
00:03:55,670 --> 00:03:56,650
I didn't do it.

88
00:03:57,080 --> 00:03:58,490
Not me!

89
00:04:02,430 --> 00:04:04,050
Your Ladyship is decisive and bold.

90
00:04:04,430 --> 00:04:06,300
Like father, like daughter!

91
00:04:06,480 --> 00:04:07,770
But she's not like you.

92
00:04:08,110 --> 00:04:10,020
She didn't let Lang Maochun truly die.

93
00:04:10,830 --> 00:04:11,930
The one that was burned

94
00:04:12,320 --> 00:04:13,610
was a corpse to begin with.

95
00:04:16,640 --> 00:04:18,580
I bet you hid a prepared body

96
00:04:18,760 --> 00:04:20,700
under the oilcloth-covered workbench.

97
00:04:25,120 --> 00:04:26,410
Using the flames

98
00:04:26,590 --> 00:04:27,740
and thick smoke as cover,

99
00:04:27,830 --> 00:04:29,380
Lang Maochun moved it out fast...

100
00:04:35,470 --> 00:04:36,260
making it look like

101
00:04:36,270 --> 00:04:37,770
he'd been pierced by bamboo ribs.

102
00:04:38,080 --> 00:04:38,970
The build

103
00:04:39,440 --> 00:04:40,500
of that body,

104
00:04:40,590 --> 00:04:42,500
and those bamboo wounds

105
00:04:42,830 --> 00:04:44,020
were convincing enough.

106
00:04:44,350 --> 00:04:46,060
But you couldn't control one surprise.

107
00:04:46,590 --> 00:04:48,530
The paste under the dragon's eyes

108
00:04:49,150 --> 00:04:50,090
is this one.

109
00:04:53,030 --> 00:04:54,410
Lang Maochun's right fingers

110
00:04:54,640 --> 00:04:55,970
were smeared with flammable oil.

111
00:04:56,270 --> 00:04:57,060
In the fire,

112
00:04:57,390 --> 00:04:58,970
they should've been badly burned.

113
00:04:59,200 --> 00:05:01,140
Yet that corpse's fingers weren't.

114
00:05:01,390 --> 00:05:02,970
I had Physician Zhao examine it.

115
00:05:03,440 --> 00:05:04,380
That body

116
00:05:04,440 --> 00:05:05,820
had been dead for days

117
00:05:05,830 --> 00:05:07,530
before it was burned.

118
00:05:07,760 --> 00:05:09,620
Your casework has improved.

119
00:05:10,320 --> 00:05:11,620
I made one mistake.

120
00:05:12,230 --> 00:05:13,060
Next

121
00:05:13,470 --> 00:05:15,210
is how you helped Lang Maochun flee.

122
00:05:15,520 --> 00:05:16,820
You must have had someone

123
00:05:17,000 --> 00:05:18,500
pour out the tung oil in advance,

124
00:05:18,680 --> 00:05:20,380
allowing him to hide inside the barrel.

125
00:05:24,960 --> 00:05:25,890
What's in that barrel?

126
00:05:26,960 --> 00:05:27,650
Tung oil!

127
00:05:28,760 --> 00:05:29,330
Hurry!

128
00:05:35,150 --> 00:05:35,740
Move!

129
00:05:45,680 --> 00:05:46,530
And right then,

130
00:05:47,560 --> 00:05:49,620
the night-soil collector you planted showed up.

131
00:05:59,790 --> 00:06:00,530
Who is it?

132
00:06:17,520 --> 00:06:18,020
Stop the cart!

133
00:06:23,150 --> 00:06:23,820
Move!

134
00:06:23,830 --> 00:06:24,330
Got it.

135
00:06:27,960 --> 00:06:28,620
Your Ladyship.

136
00:06:29,200 --> 00:06:30,530
Did you see anyone suspicious?

137
00:06:30,710 --> 00:06:31,260
No.

138
00:06:33,000 --> 00:06:33,850
Search over there.

139
00:06:33,960 --> 00:06:34,380
Understood!

140
00:06:38,680 --> 00:06:39,700
You chased after him,

141
00:06:39,960 --> 00:06:41,290
not to catch the killer,

142
00:06:41,640 --> 00:06:43,770
but to escort Lang Maochun out of the palace.

143
00:06:44,590 --> 00:06:45,740
Sharp as a needle.

144
00:06:46,230 --> 00:06:47,060
Good reasoning.

145
00:06:48,120 --> 00:06:49,270
But I don't have time

146
00:06:49,270 --> 00:06:50,450
to chat with you here.

147
00:06:50,960 --> 00:06:52,140
In two hours,

148
00:06:52,270 --> 00:06:53,180
the Grand Festival begins.

149
00:06:53,830 --> 00:06:55,850
Uncle Luo and I still have a lot to do.

150
00:06:58,960 --> 00:07:00,140
Come back with me to see His Majesty.

151
00:07:00,830 --> 00:07:01,740
I go to the palace

152
00:07:02,200 --> 00:07:03,620
to see His Majesty, of course.

153
00:07:03,830 --> 00:07:04,850
You know what I mean.

154
00:07:05,000 --> 00:07:06,620
And you know what I mean.

155
00:07:11,830 --> 00:07:13,260
I've already had this place surrounded.

156
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:15,260
Even if you kill me,

157
00:07:16,000 --> 00:07:17,290
you won't make it out that gate.

158
00:07:18,760 --> 00:07:20,140
With our skills,

159
00:07:20,470 --> 00:07:21,700
no one can stop us.

160
00:07:22,000 --> 00:07:22,530
Your Ladyship.

161
00:07:22,830 --> 00:07:24,260
Last time, if not for him

162
00:07:24,390 --> 00:07:25,500
playing generous at our expense,

163
00:07:25,520 --> 00:07:27,180
we would have had our revenge already!

164
00:07:34,350 --> 00:07:35,580
You know me.

165
00:07:36,470 --> 00:07:37,530
And I know you.

166
00:07:38,320 --> 00:07:40,330
You've always shown me mercy.

167
00:07:41,080 --> 00:07:42,090
You must come alone.

168
00:07:42,710 --> 00:07:44,770
If you only mean to stop me,

169
00:07:45,270 --> 00:07:46,620
and won't walk with me,

170
00:07:47,120 --> 00:07:48,820
then I'll find someone else to walk with.

171
00:07:49,350 --> 00:07:50,450
And if I insist on stopping you?

172
00:07:50,640 --> 00:07:51,620
Then I can only

173
00:07:51,620 --> 00:07:53,290
step over you!

174
00:07:55,230 --> 00:07:56,500
A blood-feud like this

175
00:07:57,150 --> 00:07:58,620
must be settled by my own hand.

176
00:08:02,520 --> 00:08:03,890
You're not a cold-blooded person.

177
00:08:04,880 --> 00:08:06,410
You and Consort Shu are like mother and daughter.

178
00:08:06,880 --> 00:08:08,580
You can't bear to watch him take her life.

179
00:08:08,680 --> 00:08:10,260
They're only like mother and daughter!

180
00:08:10,790 --> 00:08:12,060
But Consort Shu and the Right Chancellor

181
00:08:12,200 --> 00:08:13,410
are blood and bone.

182
00:08:13,830 --> 00:08:14,700
The Right Chancellor won't fall

183
00:08:15,150 --> 00:08:15,850
unless Consort Shu

184
00:08:15,960 --> 00:08:16,820
is removed!

185
00:08:20,880 --> 00:08:21,500
Tie him up.

186
00:08:21,830 --> 00:08:22,450
Move!

187
00:08:39,320 --> 00:08:40,100
Do you regret it?

188
00:08:43,680 --> 00:08:44,570
I can't wait.

189
00:08:48,620 --> 00:08:51,280
[Xingqing Palace]

190
00:08:51,280 --> 00:08:51,980
Stop the cart!

191
00:09:02,110 --> 00:09:03,570
Who are you from the County Princess's manor?

192
00:09:03,680 --> 00:09:05,170
Do you have a palace-issued pass?

193
00:09:06,040 --> 00:09:08,140
Even Her Ladyship's token won't get me through?

194
00:09:08,350 --> 00:09:09,750
Security is tight today.

195
00:09:09,750 --> 00:09:11,410
Without a palace-issued pass,

196
00:09:11,440 --> 00:09:12,260
you cannot enter.

197
00:09:12,750 --> 00:09:13,940
So I can't enter,

198
00:09:14,080 --> 00:09:15,410
and let Her Ladyship go in herself

199
00:09:15,630 --> 00:09:17,460
with the gifts for Consort Shu?

200
00:09:17,560 --> 00:09:18,530
You don't need to worry about that.

201
00:09:18,590 --> 00:09:19,860
The palace eunuchs will handle it.

202
00:09:21,800 --> 00:09:22,570
This face of mine

203
00:09:22,590 --> 00:09:23,920
is worth less than a pass?

204
00:09:25,200 --> 00:09:26,050
Palace rules are palace rules.

205
00:09:28,080 --> 00:09:29,170
This brat doesn't know better.

206
00:09:29,630 --> 00:09:31,140
Your Ladyship, please forgive him.

207
00:09:31,440 --> 00:09:32,100
This way, please!

208
00:09:33,200 --> 00:09:34,380
We haven't searched the cart.

209
00:09:39,900 --> 00:09:42,540
[Xingqing Palace]

210
00:09:57,280 --> 00:09:57,930
Move it away.

211
00:10:09,990 --> 00:10:10,500
Boss,

212
00:10:10,830 --> 00:10:11,650
what's this?

213
00:10:12,800 --> 00:10:13,380
Put it down!

214
00:10:13,630 --> 00:10:14,410
We need to check it!

215
00:10:14,470 --> 00:10:15,170
This is my gift

216
00:10:15,200 --> 00:10:16,380
for Consort Shu.

217
00:10:16,560 --> 00:10:17,890
Let Her Highness open it herself.

218
00:10:19,630 --> 00:10:20,170
Understood.

219
00:10:22,800 --> 00:10:23,530
Your Ladyship,

220
00:10:23,830 --> 00:10:25,050
if you need anything,

221
00:10:25,320 --> 00:10:26,170
just give the word.

222
00:10:30,440 --> 00:10:31,570
You guys, go check over there.

223
00:10:31,830 --> 00:10:32,340
Understood!

224
00:10:37,200 --> 00:10:38,930
I know something will happen tonight.

225
00:10:39,230 --> 00:10:40,460
Inform me once you learn anything.

226
00:10:41,080 --> 00:10:41,930
I can help too.

227
00:10:44,890 --> 00:10:46,500
Then help check over there.

228
00:11:00,710 --> 00:11:01,340
Boss,

229
00:11:01,750 --> 00:11:02,690
Mr. Xiao said

230
00:11:02,690 --> 00:11:03,610
the killer might

231
00:11:03,610 --> 00:11:05,020
strike again tonight.

232
00:11:05,470 --> 00:11:06,890
I've been on edge all day.

233
00:11:07,360 --> 00:11:08,480
Look, my hands are shaking.

234
00:11:16,730 --> 00:11:17,460
It's cold.

235
00:11:18,630 --> 00:11:19,410
You're dressed too lightly.

236
00:11:20,350 --> 00:11:21,460
Of course your hands are shaking.

237
00:11:22,230 --> 00:11:23,850
I'm on duty.

238
00:11:24,080 --> 00:11:25,890
You're making me embarrassed.

239
00:11:25,990 --> 00:11:26,690
Why be embarrassed?

240
00:11:27,470 --> 00:11:28,290
If you freeze,

241
00:11:28,590 --> 00:11:29,530
you can't even wield your sword.

242
00:11:31,400 --> 00:11:32,050
Boss,

243
00:11:32,590 --> 00:11:33,380
you're really kind.

244
00:11:35,630 --> 00:11:36,410
Thank you.

245
00:11:37,110 --> 00:11:37,810
Tonight,

246
00:11:38,630 --> 00:11:39,980
I can't keep watch with you.

247
00:11:40,440 --> 00:11:42,380
With you beside His Majesty and Consort Shu,

248
00:11:42,380 --> 00:11:43,500
I'll feel more at ease.

249
00:11:52,280 --> 00:11:53,930
He's in charge of the gifts for His Majesty

250
00:11:53,990 --> 00:11:54,810
and Consort Shu.

251
00:11:54,990 --> 00:11:56,220
Treat him as you would treat me.

252
00:11:57,160 --> 00:11:57,690
Understood!

253
00:12:08,960 --> 00:12:10,860
Enjoy the night.

254
00:12:15,320 --> 00:12:16,860
The Protector-General has sent troops

255
00:12:16,920 --> 00:12:18,220
to station outside Chunming Gate.

256
00:12:18,470 --> 00:12:19,810
We're waiting for your order, Master.

257
00:12:29,160 --> 00:12:30,170
Has the evening drum sounded?

258
00:12:31,400 --> 00:12:32,260
It's the start of You Hour.

259
00:12:34,920 --> 00:12:36,140
Wait a little longer.

260
00:12:40,990 --> 00:12:42,810
Pass it on. Keep strict watch.

261
00:12:42,920 --> 00:12:43,650
Understood!

262
00:12:56,960 --> 00:12:57,570
Wuren.

263
00:12:59,040 --> 00:12:59,690
How is it?

264
00:13:00,230 --> 00:13:01,050
No sign of anything.

265
00:13:12,680 --> 00:13:13,500
Go check over there.

266
00:13:22,590 --> 00:13:23,460
What time is it?

267
00:13:26,470 --> 00:13:27,690
The second ke of You Hour.

268
00:13:28,750 --> 00:13:29,500
Master,

269
00:13:29,990 --> 00:13:31,980
His Majesty will never summon you

270
00:13:32,110 --> 00:13:33,980
for tonight's Grand Festival.

271
00:13:45,990 --> 00:13:46,650
You may go now.

272
00:13:48,040 --> 00:13:48,650
Master,

273
00:13:49,320 --> 00:13:50,410
we really can't wait any longer.

274
00:13:51,320 --> 00:13:53,500
The Imperial Guards have doubled inside the palace.

275
00:13:53,590 --> 00:13:54,530
Consort Shu will be in danger

276
00:13:54,590 --> 00:13:56,050
at the Grand Festival.

277
00:13:56,630 --> 00:13:57,410
Move now,

278
00:13:58,080 --> 00:13:59,220
or it'll be too late!

279
00:14:02,470 --> 00:14:04,140
We siblings

280
00:14:06,040 --> 00:14:07,410
have served His Majesty

281
00:14:08,470 --> 00:14:10,690
with all our hearts for decades.

282
00:14:11,560 --> 00:14:12,990
As long as His Majesty remembers

283
00:14:12,990 --> 00:14:14,380
the bond we once had,

284
00:14:15,710 --> 00:14:17,770
I won't take it too far.

285
00:14:18,560 --> 00:14:19,620
Tonight,

286
00:14:20,280 --> 00:14:22,050
if I lead troops into the palace,

287
00:14:22,400 --> 00:14:24,220
whether to purge the traitors

288
00:14:24,630 --> 00:14:26,410
or to save Consort Shu,

289
00:14:26,680 --> 00:14:28,340
in His Majesty's eyes,

290
00:14:28,750 --> 00:14:30,340
it would be treason.

291
00:14:36,750 --> 00:14:37,690
So...

292
00:14:39,680 --> 00:14:40,650
let's wait a little longer.

293
00:14:47,630 --> 00:14:48,500
A guest is here.

294
00:14:56,630 --> 00:14:58,020
Chen Luo has entered the palace with Her Ladyship.

295
00:14:58,320 --> 00:14:59,690
Everything is in place.

296
00:15:00,560 --> 00:15:01,500
And the Right Chancellor

297
00:15:01,630 --> 00:15:02,620
is about to boil over.

298
00:15:04,870 --> 00:15:06,340
Everything is ready.

299
00:15:06,750 --> 00:15:08,050
And the time has come.

300
00:15:09,080 --> 00:15:09,980
Let's enter the palace.

301
00:15:10,110 --> 00:15:10,650
Understood!

302
00:16:09,700 --> 00:16:11,160
[Xingqing Palace]

303
00:16:11,160 --> 00:16:11,740
Stop right there!

304
00:16:12,280 --> 00:16:12,860
Deputy Director Xiao.

305
00:16:15,750 --> 00:16:19,380
Consort Shu is about to dance!

306
00:17:31,160 --> 00:17:32,020
Mr. Xiao?

307
00:17:32,120 --> 00:17:33,090
Why are you here so late?

308
00:17:33,120 --> 00:17:34,090
Have you seen Chen Luo?

309
00:17:34,470 --> 00:17:35,180
Chen Luo?

310
00:17:35,440 --> 00:17:36,370
He's the Celestial Lord.

311
00:17:36,470 --> 00:17:37,500
He should be in the palace right now.

312
00:18:14,640 --> 00:18:16,500
Why are the fireworks lit at this time?

313
00:18:16,500 --> 00:18:17,530
They must have made a mistake.

314
00:18:20,750 --> 00:18:21,770
"Phoenix Dances Across the Nine Heavens.

315
00:18:22,310 --> 00:18:23,500
Venus Shines in Tandem."

316
00:18:24,550 --> 00:18:25,500
What's that supposed to mean?

317
00:18:27,270 --> 00:18:28,130
Your Majesty,

318
00:18:28,230 --> 00:18:29,420
it was supposed to be

319
00:18:29,550 --> 00:18:31,420
"Dragon Roams the Four Seas."

320
00:18:31,470 --> 00:18:32,220
How could it...

321
00:18:32,960 --> 00:18:33,900
Why are you still standing there?

322
00:18:33,900 --> 00:18:35,290
Go check it now!

323
00:18:35,600 --> 00:18:36,700
Go, now!

324
00:18:36,960 --> 00:18:37,530
Understood.

325
00:19:05,990 --> 00:19:07,020
"Phoenix Dances Across the Nine Heavens."

326
00:19:08,120 --> 00:19:09,090
In the whole sky,

327
00:19:09,200 --> 00:19:10,220
only one phoenix reigns.

328
00:19:10,920 --> 00:19:11,530
Mr. Xiao?

329
00:19:12,070 --> 00:19:13,050
They're using

330
00:19:13,510 --> 00:19:14,470
Grand Festival fireworks

331
00:19:14,470 --> 00:19:15,660
to brand Consort Shu as one

332
00:19:15,840 --> 00:19:16,900
who'd upend the realm.

333
00:19:17,960 --> 00:19:18,940
They're using His Majesty's hand

334
00:19:19,960 --> 00:19:21,130
to have her executed.

335
00:19:22,790 --> 00:19:24,420
Whoever set up those fireworks deserves death.

336
00:19:24,550 --> 00:19:25,260
I'll go check it.

337
00:19:26,510 --> 00:19:27,500
It's Her Ladyship.

338
00:19:28,550 --> 00:19:30,020
Her Ladyship prepared the fireworks.

339
00:19:30,680 --> 00:19:32,180
And there was someone with her.

340
00:19:32,600 --> 00:19:34,260
I thought he was just a servant.

341
00:19:34,790 --> 00:19:35,500
It's all my fault.

342
00:19:35,680 --> 00:19:36,610
I let my guard down.

343
00:19:37,600 --> 00:19:38,420
Her Ladyship?

344
00:19:39,120 --> 00:19:40,180
Why would she do this?

345
00:19:41,640 --> 00:19:42,610
She wants Consort Shu dead?

346
00:19:43,510 --> 00:19:44,180
Let's go!

347
00:19:50,920 --> 00:19:52,460
So that's it.

348
00:19:58,440 --> 00:19:59,570
At tonight's Grand Festival,

349
00:20:00,030 --> 00:20:01,290
the Cui clan faces a great disaster.

350
00:20:13,840 --> 00:20:15,050
How is it in the palace?

351
00:20:15,880 --> 00:20:16,600
His Majesty is furious.

352
00:20:16,600 --> 00:20:17,770
He may order Consort Shu executed.

353
00:20:23,710 --> 00:20:24,220
Report!

354
00:20:24,400 --> 00:20:25,660
No idea how the news got out,

355
00:20:25,790 --> 00:20:26,660
but a squad of Imperial Guards

356
00:20:26,710 --> 00:20:27,980
is heading this way!

357
00:20:30,790 --> 00:20:32,500
You can put Consort Shu on a pedestal,

358
00:20:33,400 --> 00:20:34,940
but forget about bringing her down.

359
00:20:35,840 --> 00:20:37,220
Trying to use this

360
00:20:37,990 --> 00:20:41,420
to brand her a traitor

361
00:20:41,470 --> 00:20:43,050
and wipe out my clan?

362
00:20:44,200 --> 00:20:46,330
Wrong move!

363
00:20:48,680 --> 00:20:50,220
His Majesty is blind.

364
00:20:51,880 --> 00:20:54,370
He won't even give me a chance to explain,

365
00:20:55,160 --> 00:20:57,610
and already wants me wiped out!

366
00:20:58,990 --> 00:20:59,610
Fine...

367
00:21:00,440 --> 00:21:02,500
since you drive me to rebel,

368
00:21:02,530 --> 00:21:03,660
I have no choice!

369
00:21:04,960 --> 00:21:06,660
I'll give you what you want.

370
00:21:07,270 --> 00:21:08,610
I'll oblige you.

371
00:21:11,360 --> 00:21:12,500
Kill!

372
00:21:12,550 --> 00:21:13,610
Kill!

373
00:21:16,980 --> 00:21:18,260
[Chunming Gate]

374
00:21:37,160 --> 00:21:37,940
Cui Minzhong!

375
00:21:38,470 --> 00:21:40,500
You dare raise troops

376
00:21:40,500 --> 00:21:41,530
at the palace gates!

377
00:21:42,370 --> 00:21:43,250
Today,

378
00:21:43,470 --> 00:21:44,780
for His Majesty,

379
00:21:45,360 --> 00:21:46,730
I'll wipe out you rebels!

380
00:21:48,270 --> 00:21:49,900
Who do you think you are?

381
00:21:50,290 --> 00:21:52,040
You framed me first,

382
00:21:52,770 --> 00:21:54,360
then claim you're quelling rebels.

383
00:21:54,740 --> 00:21:56,230
You're the real villain here.

384
00:21:56,910 --> 00:21:58,350
I may not be a general,

385
00:21:59,680 --> 00:22:00,770
but I'll still fight

386
00:22:00,770 --> 00:22:02,980
for this loyal heart of mine!

387
00:22:03,640 --> 00:22:04,410
Kill!

388
00:22:04,410 --> 00:22:05,820
Kill!

389
00:22:34,730 --> 00:22:35,700
Send word back to the palace:

390
00:22:36,250 --> 00:22:37,590
The Right Chancellor has rebelled!

391
00:22:37,680 --> 00:22:38,220
Understood!

392
00:22:45,080 --> 00:22:45,980
It's done.

393
00:22:46,330 --> 00:22:47,390
Once the sign goes up,

394
00:22:47,770 --> 00:22:49,420
Consort Shu is as good as dead!

395
00:22:50,080 --> 00:22:50,830
The Cui clan

396
00:22:51,210 --> 00:22:51,940
is finished!

397
00:22:55,210 --> 00:22:56,590
Congrats, Commandant Chen.

398
00:22:56,880 --> 00:22:58,140
Your vengeance is complete.

399
00:22:59,290 --> 00:23:00,220
Congrats, My Lord!

400
00:23:08,210 --> 00:23:09,460
Anyone who tries to stop me

401
00:23:09,570 --> 00:23:10,270
dies!

402
00:23:10,970 --> 00:23:11,870
Open the gate!

403
00:23:23,770 --> 00:23:25,350
His Majesty has an edict:

404
00:23:25,680 --> 00:23:26,980
One more step,

405
00:23:28,010 --> 00:23:29,460
and you walk to your death!

406
00:23:54,160 --> 00:23:55,220
This is...

407
00:23:56,290 --> 00:23:57,590
Her Ladyship didn't kill Consort Shu?

408
00:24:02,360 --> 00:24:04,980
Your Majesty, look!

409
00:24:05,160 --> 00:24:08,460
"Phoenix Blesses a Thousand Generations.

410
00:24:08,810 --> 00:24:12,110
Dragon Soars to the Highest Heaven!"

411
00:24:12,330 --> 00:24:14,740
A dragon and a phoenix in harmony.

412
00:24:14,840 --> 00:24:16,460
May Great Tang

413
00:24:16,530 --> 00:24:20,140
prosper for endless generations!

414
00:24:20,140 --> 00:24:21,100
[Li Qiang, Crown Prince]

415
00:24:46,290 --> 00:24:47,420
So that's it...

416
00:24:52,880 --> 00:24:54,830
So that's it.

417
00:24:55,250 --> 00:24:57,220
This whole puzzle

418
00:24:57,680 --> 00:25:00,630
was to force me to raise troops.

419
00:25:02,570 --> 00:25:04,870
What a fine scheme.

420
00:25:05,680 --> 00:25:06,420
Xie Binglin.

421
00:25:07,050 --> 00:25:07,790
Where are you?

422
00:25:09,880 --> 00:25:10,660
Master!

423
00:25:15,330 --> 00:25:16,660
Turn back while you can.

424
00:25:16,840 --> 00:25:19,140
There may still be a way out!

425
00:25:21,600 --> 00:25:23,980
Trying to make me surrender?

426
00:25:25,080 --> 00:25:26,630
You think you're worthy?

427
00:25:33,600 --> 00:25:35,460
I have no way back now.

428
00:25:35,770 --> 00:25:36,660
Kill them!

429
00:25:36,970 --> 00:25:37,590
Fire!

430
00:25:43,290 --> 00:25:46,070
Kill!

431
00:26:37,840 --> 00:26:39,270
I want to see His Majesty...

432
00:26:39,920 --> 00:26:41,500
I want to see Consort Shu!

433
00:26:45,770 --> 00:26:46,900
Today,

434
00:26:47,360 --> 00:26:49,220
even if I die,

435
00:26:49,680 --> 00:26:52,630
I won't die at the hands

436
00:26:53,840 --> 00:26:55,830
of you ants!

437
00:27:18,330 --> 00:27:19,700
The palace has been unsettled of late.

438
00:27:20,250 --> 00:27:21,390
And that nursery rhyme

439
00:27:21,440 --> 00:27:23,390
going around in the capital bears

440
00:27:23,640 --> 00:27:24,830
sinister intent.

441
00:27:25,120 --> 00:27:26,940
I saw enemies in every shadow.

442
00:27:27,490 --> 00:27:28,940
I nearly took it out on you.

443
00:27:29,360 --> 00:27:30,180
Please,

444
00:27:30,600 --> 00:27:31,790
don't blame me.

445
00:27:32,880 --> 00:27:34,980
I understand Your Majesty's heart.

446
00:27:35,680 --> 00:27:37,310
How could I blame Your Majesty?

447
00:27:44,210 --> 00:27:44,900
Your Majesty.

448
00:27:46,370 --> 00:27:48,270
The Right Chancellor led troops and forced the gate.

449
00:27:48,300 --> 00:27:49,630
He awaits your sentence outside.

450
00:27:52,120 --> 00:27:52,870
Let him in.

451
00:28:01,680 --> 00:28:02,310
Your Majesty.

452
00:28:02,730 --> 00:28:04,390
Cui Minzhong colluded with rebel forces

453
00:28:04,440 --> 00:28:05,500
and charged the palace gate.

454
00:28:05,770 --> 00:28:06,700
He committed treason,

455
00:28:06,970 --> 00:28:08,070
seeking to overthrow the realm.

456
00:28:08,360 --> 00:28:08,900
Now,

457
00:28:09,120 --> 00:28:10,270
the rebel has been seized.

458
00:28:10,440 --> 00:28:12,220
And his accomplices have all been captured.

459
00:28:15,080 --> 00:28:15,700
Let go of me!

460
00:28:34,490 --> 00:28:35,110
Your Majesty,

461
00:28:36,730 --> 00:28:38,390
this humble minister can finally

462
00:28:39,530 --> 00:28:41,110
see your face again...

463
00:28:42,680 --> 00:28:43,740
Cui Minzhong,

464
00:28:44,530 --> 00:28:45,790
you've grown bold, huh?

465
00:28:52,290 --> 00:28:53,070
Your Majesty,

466
00:28:53,840 --> 00:28:54,830
I'm wronged.

467
00:28:56,880 --> 00:28:58,030
Look at you.

468
00:28:58,640 --> 00:28:59,790
The evidence is solid.

469
00:29:00,050 --> 00:29:01,180
And you still want to argue?

470
00:29:02,330 --> 00:29:03,980
I obeyed your command,

471
00:29:04,680 --> 00:29:06,550
copied scriptures at home to repent,

472
00:29:07,360 --> 00:29:09,140
and never dared cross the line.

473
00:29:10,730 --> 00:29:11,700
But someone

474
00:29:12,330 --> 00:29:14,180
wouldn't let me go.

475
00:29:14,240 --> 00:29:15,980
They wanted me dead!

476
00:29:16,570 --> 00:29:17,900
I'm not afraid to die.

477
00:29:18,680 --> 00:29:20,460
I'm afraid someone used a nursery rhyme

478
00:29:20,460 --> 00:29:21,670
to spread rumors,

479
00:29:22,080 --> 00:29:23,420
using Consort Shu

480
00:29:23,970 --> 00:29:25,110
to sow discord.

481
00:29:25,600 --> 00:29:26,460
They wanted

482
00:29:26,530 --> 00:29:27,980
Your Majesty to suspect

483
00:29:28,160 --> 00:29:29,630
this loyal minister!

484
00:29:30,360 --> 00:29:31,940
I only doubted you,

485
00:29:32,210 --> 00:29:33,270
and you wanted to kill me?

486
00:29:33,840 --> 00:29:35,700
Cui Minzhong,

487
00:29:36,120 --> 00:29:38,140
so loyal, aren't you?

488
00:29:38,600 --> 00:29:39,740
My blade cut down

489
00:29:40,240 --> 00:29:41,520
what blocked my road

490
00:29:41,520 --> 00:29:43,180
to see Your Majesty.

491
00:29:43,600 --> 00:29:44,740
It severed

492
00:29:45,970 --> 00:29:48,180
your misunderstanding of me.

493
00:29:49,210 --> 00:29:50,900
It's true I brought troops into the palace.

494
00:29:51,330 --> 00:29:52,420
But only this way

495
00:29:52,530 --> 00:29:53,420
could I

496
00:29:53,420 --> 00:29:56,030
make Your Majesty see my sincere heart!

497
00:29:56,880 --> 00:29:57,690
This minister

498
00:29:58,050 --> 00:29:59,180
was forced into it.

499
00:29:59,210 --> 00:30:00,310
I had no choice.

500
00:30:01,770 --> 00:30:03,460
The one who set this up

501
00:30:05,330 --> 00:30:07,900
truly means harm to Great Tang.

502
00:30:08,160 --> 00:30:09,980
They deserve death!

503
00:30:10,650 --> 00:30:12,210
You raised the troops.

504
00:30:12,530 --> 00:30:13,500
And you got yourself

505
00:30:13,600 --> 00:30:14,940
covered in blood.

506
00:30:15,730 --> 00:30:16,390
And you still

507
00:30:17,120 --> 00:30:18,030
want to pin this crime

508
00:30:18,030 --> 00:30:19,550
on someone who doesn't exist?

509
00:30:21,570 --> 00:30:22,390
At first,

510
00:30:23,490 --> 00:30:24,500
I couldn't understand

511
00:30:25,400 --> 00:30:27,590
how someone could be so vicious,

512
00:30:28,080 --> 00:30:29,180
hate this minister

513
00:30:29,360 --> 00:30:30,420
to such a degree.

514
00:30:31,330 --> 00:30:32,270
But today...

515
00:30:35,400 --> 00:30:37,030
I finally understand.

516
00:30:38,010 --> 00:30:39,460
The one behind it

517
00:30:40,160 --> 00:30:41,550
has a name.

518
00:30:42,680 --> 00:30:43,790
She is...

519
00:30:44,250 --> 00:30:45,310
Li Peiyi!

520
00:30:59,330 --> 00:31:00,390
Cui Minzhong,

521
00:31:01,210 --> 00:31:02,660
was tonight's Grand Festival

522
00:31:03,210 --> 00:31:04,270
to your liking?

523
00:31:05,730 --> 00:31:06,460
Your Majesty.

524
00:31:07,120 --> 00:31:07,980
You saw it.

525
00:31:08,570 --> 00:31:09,500
It was her.

526
00:31:09,770 --> 00:31:10,810
That cursed lone star

527
00:31:10,810 --> 00:31:12,460
is dissatisfied with Your Majesty's punishment of me,

528
00:31:12,530 --> 00:31:14,030
and wants me dead!

529
00:31:14,400 --> 00:31:16,350
She not only drove a wedge between us,

530
00:31:16,400 --> 00:31:18,660
she also used my love for Consort Shu

531
00:31:18,970 --> 00:31:20,210
to make me think

532
00:31:20,210 --> 00:31:22,590
Your Majesty meant to kill her!

533
00:31:22,680 --> 00:31:23,740
Don't smear her!

534
00:31:30,920 --> 00:31:31,420
Your Majesty.

535
00:31:33,250 --> 00:31:34,870
The culprit behind the palace murders

536
00:31:35,010 --> 00:31:35,900
has been identified.

537
00:31:36,120 --> 00:31:37,390
We're just waiting to catch him red-handed.

538
00:31:37,770 --> 00:31:39,110
It has nothing to do with Her Ladyship.

539
00:31:40,570 --> 00:31:41,590
Silence!

540
00:31:44,160 --> 00:31:45,630
You and Li Peiyi

541
00:31:46,210 --> 00:31:48,070
are in league.

542
00:31:49,360 --> 00:31:50,500
You had a hand

543
00:31:50,730 --> 00:31:52,010
in framing me!

544
00:31:52,010 --> 00:31:53,550
How dare you vouch for her?

545
00:31:56,440 --> 00:31:57,900
You've always had a silver tongue.

546
00:31:58,680 --> 00:32:00,070
Now the evidence is ironclad.

547
00:32:00,070 --> 00:32:01,270
So I'm curious

548
00:32:01,570 --> 00:32:03,500
how you will twist the truth.

549
00:32:04,050 --> 00:32:04,970
This woman

550
00:32:04,970 --> 00:32:07,070
has plotted against me at every turn.

551
00:32:07,680 --> 00:32:08,460
Your Majesty,

552
00:32:08,840 --> 00:32:10,590
the recent murders in the palace,

553
00:32:11,010 --> 00:32:12,140
and that nursery rhyme

554
00:32:12,160 --> 00:32:13,460
spreading through the capital

555
00:32:13,530 --> 00:32:15,310
must be all her doing!

556
00:32:17,690 --> 00:32:19,040
If I hadn't gone this far,

557
00:32:20,280 --> 00:32:22,210
how could I see Your Majesty again,

558
00:32:24,600 --> 00:32:26,270
and see my little sister again?

559
00:32:29,050 --> 00:32:29,740
Little sister...

560
00:32:30,810 --> 00:32:31,550
Consort Shu...

561
00:32:32,400 --> 00:32:34,740
you know me!

562
00:32:35,400 --> 00:32:36,700
When have I

563
00:32:37,160 --> 00:32:38,180
ever been disloyal

564
00:32:39,210 --> 00:32:41,700
to Your Majesty or to Tang?

565
00:32:47,080 --> 00:32:47,830
My beloved,

566
00:32:49,080 --> 00:32:49,790
in your opinion,

567
00:32:50,530 --> 00:32:51,350
what should we do?

568
00:33:04,440 --> 00:33:05,460
Cui Minzhong

569
00:33:05,920 --> 00:33:06,980
has committed treason.

570
00:33:07,490 --> 00:33:09,140
This is a minister's greatest crime.

571
00:33:09,920 --> 00:33:12,110
As the sister of a traitor,

572
00:33:12,600 --> 00:33:15,310
I'm willing to accept the punishment with him,

573
00:33:16,290 --> 00:33:17,350
without complaint or regret.

574
00:33:17,540 --> 00:33:23,900
♪Gazing at the moon from a distant terrace♪

575
00:33:26,290 --> 00:33:27,390
My beloved, please rise.

576
00:33:31,740 --> 00:33:38,100
♪The injustice in the world remains unrighted♪

577
00:33:38,120 --> 00:33:39,660
Get back to your manor

578
00:33:39,970 --> 00:33:41,030
and await judgment!

579
00:33:43,880 --> 00:33:44,590
Your Majesty...

580
00:33:45,640 --> 00:33:46,310
Your Majesty!

581
